  "body": "### Browser window does not \"turn\" orientation to landscape mode when device is turned on its side. \n### User Story\nAs a user I want to view the DApp in \"landscape\" mode to complete a task in a DApp, or view more efficiently. This does not happen when I turn my device. \n\n### Description\n_Type_: Bug\n\n### when opening a DApp I want to be able to rotate my screen into landscape mode when turned on its side so for better mobile viewing\n_Summary_: Back reference - https://stackoverflow.com/questions/4917664/detect-viewport-orientation-if-orientation-is-portrait-display-alert-message-ad\n\n#### Expected behavior\n ### I want to turn my phone and view landscape mode when device is turned. \n\n#### Actual behavior\n ### Viewpoint stays same no matter which way device is turned \n\n### Reproduction\n # \n\n* Open DApp\n* Browser window opened , turn device to side \n\n### Solution\n### Create portrait mode availability in browser\n### Additional Information\n[comment]: # na\n\n* Status version: ...\n[comment]: # (Android or iOS.)\n* Operating System: Both\n#### Logs\n\n[comment]: # \n\n```\n...\n```",
